  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A line of pure destruction 60 feet long and 10 feet wide emanates from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the line must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 6d6 fire or lightning damage and is Dazed on a failed save, or half as much damage and no other effects on a success. The destructive energy disintegrates Tiny objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2d6.</p>",
